extendedInfo.description: Learn some great new Street Dancing moves and jumps with this free app.Street dance is used to describe dance styles that developed outside of dance studios on the streets, in schoolyards and at nightclubs.Street dancers often make up the routine as they go, and encourage the crowd and the other dancers to interact with them. Street dance is also used to describe all the hip hop and funk dance styles that began appearing in the United States in the 1970s. Most of these styles such as breakdance, popping, locking, hip hop and house dance, are still alive and evolving within the hip hop culture of today, and are seen regularly in music videos.Classes are creative and blend original hip hop styles fused with modern commercial moves to the latest hip hop controversial beats!This Apps Contains Following Features:1.Beginners2.Advanced3.Movements4.Tutorials5.World Street Dance6.Jumps7.Video TutorialsTutorial Vidos:1.How To Dance Hip-Hop Like Justin Timberlake2.How To Grind3.Dance Moves: An Emergency Guide For Men4.Breakdancing: Basic Moves5.How To Dance: Krumping6.How To Breakdance For Beginners7.How To Pop And Lock8.How To Dance The Electric Slide9.How To Breakdance - Windmill10.How To House Dance11.How To Swipe12.How To Breakdance Step By Step13.How To Dance: Krumping14.How To Do A Wave15.How To Dance Hip-Hop Like Justin Timberlake16.How To Jumpstyle17.How To Crip Walk Step By Step18.How To Breakdance - Windmill19.How To Do Hip Hop Dance MovesKey words:Street Dance, Street Dancing, Dance, Hiphop,Hiphop Dance,Dance,Dance Tutorials, Dance Music, Ringtone, karnam style song, gangnam style,Breakdancing: Basic Moves,Breakdancing, Belly Dance, famous Dance, Ballroom Dance, 80s Dance, Street dance
